Introduction to nursing administration　 
護理行政概論
Instructor: 
林秋芬
Chiou-Fen Lin
College of Nursing
            Taipei Medical University
Course Structure: 2 Hours per week
 TMU Podcast 播客





Image courtesy of eduCommons (275px x 275px)
Course Description
This course is introduction to nursing administration. Course design is follow in management 5 steps. The content include: planning, organization, human resource management, leading and controlling.
本課程旨在介紹護理行政之基本概論， 課程設計依管理五步驟進行，內容包括：規劃、組織、人員管理、領導和控制等。


開課系所:護理學系
開課年級: 4
學分:2







